        {
            "text": "In a recent study revealed that, due to the treatment protocol, patients with hypertension, or diabetes, who are treated with ACE2-increasing drugs, are at higher risk for severe COVID-19 infection [20] . Due to the effect of fasting on Diabetes, Blood fat and Hypertension, rigorous Journal Pre-proof J o u r n a l P r e -p r o o f studies are needed to find the effect of fasting on reducing/increasing the chance of a healthy person to becoming ill.",
